## Disclaimer

This software is designed to optimize macOS performance through system cleanup
and maintenance operations. While every effort has been made to ensure safe
operation:

- Always backup important data before running optimization scripts
- Test scripts in a safe environment before production use
- The authors are not responsible for any data loss or system damage
- Use at your own discretion and risk

## Safety Features

The software includes multiple safety mechanisms:
- Automatic backup creation before destructive operations
- Comprehensive logging of all actions
- Conservative default settings
- Rollback capabilities for most operations

